nodes.text: The Unseen Planets of Episode II

The Unseen Planets of Episode II was an article written by Daniel Wallace for Star Wars Insider 80, which featured five planets (and moons) that were only in Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones through dialogue. Note: One of them, Shadda-Bi-Boran was only inferred to, not heard, and in a deleted scene of the film.
These are five worlds were explored in the article. They are accompanied by the quote that mentioned them in the film.
